Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.templates

The low-level model (the template and its elements) and the template processor.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActionContext
    The context in which an action is created and executed.
    ActionElement
    A template element that executes an action.
    ExpressionElement
    A template element that evaluates an expression and writes the result to the writer.
    Template
    A template.
    TemplateElement
    A part of a template.
    TemplateElementFactory
    Used by parsers to create various kinds of template elements.
    TextElement
    A template element that writes text to the writer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTemplateElement
    Helps implementing the template element interface.
    ActionContributionDescriptor
    Describes an action contribution.
    ActionDescriptor
    Describes an action.
    DefaultActionContext
    The action context implementation that is used by the default action element.
    DefaultActionElement
    The default action element implementation.
    DefaultExpressionElement
    The default expression element implementation.
    DefaultTemplateElementFactory
    A template element factory that creates default template elements.
    DefaultTextElement
    The default text element implementation.
    TemplateBuilder
    Builds a template.
    TemplateInformation
    Information about a template that is being processed.
    TemplateProcessor
    Processes a single template.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ActionPhase
    The life cycle of an action.
